<h2 id="oligo-datasets">Oligo datasets</h2>

<p>We have developed oligo datasets for several plant species. The datasets currently cover six popular plant species.<br />
The oligo datasets is available <a href="http://bioinfor.yzu.edu.cn/Download/oligo_datasets"><strong>here</strong></a>.</p>
